@# Simple Luma Template Example

Hello, $name!

Your profile:
- Name: $user.name
- Email: ${user.email | default("not provided")}

@if user.is_admin
  You have admin privileges.
@else
  You are a regular user.
@end

Your items:
@for item in items
  ${loop.index}. $item
@else
  No items found.
@end

Filters demo:
- Uppercase: ${name | upper}
- Default: ${missing | default("fallback value")}
- Length: ${items | length} items

@# Escaped dollar sign: $$100
Price: $$100
